  "elements": {
    "inscriptions": [
      {
        "id": "insc-2",
        "text": "I used to live my life in fear",
        "font": {
          "family": "French Script",
          "size_px": 36
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 62.599,
          "y_px": -200.667
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-3",
        "text": "Was worried all the time. From waking up to laying down",
        "font": {
          "family": "French Script",
          "size_px": 36
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -7.949,
          "y_px": -182
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-5",
        "text": "I had no peace of mind. The world became a darkened place",
        "font": {
          "family": "French Script",
          "size_px": 36
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -0.994,
          "y_px": -167.333
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-7",
        "text": "a struggle without end and although bitter times those",
        "font": {
          "family": "French Script",
          "size_px": 40
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 0.994,
          "y_px": -151.333
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-8",
        "text": "were the days that I began to understand I was only a man",
        "font": {
          "family": "French Script",
          "size_px": 36
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 1.987,
          "y_px": -135.333
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-11",
        "text": "I grew up singing songs in church with questions on my mind",
        "font": {
          "family": "French Script",
          "size_px": 35
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 0.994,
          "y_px": -118.667
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-13",
        "text": "Then turn my back and ran away from God who gave me life",
        "font": {
          "family": "French Script",
          "size_px": 35
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -0.994,
          "y_px": -101.333
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-15",
        "text": "Then one night His presence fell, I wept and shook and knelt",
        "font": {
          "family": "French Script",
          "size_px": 34
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -2.981,
          "y_px": -86.667
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-17",
        "text": "I fell down and cried Dear Jesus will you rescue me again?",
        "font": {
          "family": "French Script",
          "size_px": 36
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -0.994,
          "y_px": -71.333
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-18",
        "text": "I understand, I&apos;m only a man. And He said,\"What will it",
        "font": {
          "family": "French Script",
          "size_px": 36
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -1.987,
          "y_px": -56.667
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-20",
        "text": "be now will you choose Me or keep swimming upstream now",
        "font": {
          "family": "French Script",
          "size_px": 36
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 1.987,
          "y_px": -42.667
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-23",
        "text": "I&apos;ve been inside your head hearing you scream out,Well here",
        "font": {
          "family": "French Script",
          "size_px": 36
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 0,
          "y_px": -27.333
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-24",
        "text": "I am just, take my hand and I&apos;ll take out all the things",
        "font": {
          "family": "French Script",
          "size_px": 36
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -0.994,
          "y_px": -12
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-25",
        "text": "along with all of the fear, all of the fear\"",
        "font": {
          "family": "French Script",
          "size_px": 36
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 0,
          "y_px": 8
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-26",
        "text": "I&apos;ll give you my burdens Lord",
        "font": {
          "family": "French Script",
          "size_px": 36
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 0,
          "y_px": 28
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-27",
        "text": "\"I&apos;ll give you peace\"",
        "font": {
          "family": "French Script",
          "size_px": 36
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 0,
          "y_px": 48
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-28",
        "text": "All of my desires? \"I&apos;ll give you what you need\"",
        "font": {
          "family": "French Script",
          "size_px": 36
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 0,
          "y_px": 68
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-29",
        "text": "And what about these chains Lord?",
        "font": {
          "family": "French Script",
          "size_px": 50
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 2.981,
          "y_px": 84.667
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-30",
        "text": "\"I&apos;ll set you free\"",
        "font": {
          "family": "French Script",
          "size_px": 36
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 0.994,
          "y_px": 102.667
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-31",
        "text": "But they&apos;re so heavy Lord",
        "font": {
          "family": "French Script",
          "size_px": 36
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 3.975,
          "y_px": 118.667
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-32",
        "text": "\"Lay them at my feet\"",
        "font": {
          "family": "French Script",
          "size_px": 36
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 0,
          "y_px": 136
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-33",
        "text": "I&apos;ll lay them at your feet Lord",
        "font": {
          "family": "French Script",
          "size_px": 36
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 0.994,
          "y_px": 153.333
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-34",
        "text": "Just promise You won&apos;t leave",
        "font": {
          "family": "French Script",
          "size_px": 36
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 2.981,
          "y_px": 169.333
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-35",
        "text": "\"I&apos;ll never leave\"",
        "font": {
          "family": "French Script",
          "size_px": 50
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -0.994,
          "y_px": 190
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-36",
        "text": "So where do I go from here Lord?",
        "font": {
          "family": "French Script",
          "size_px": 36
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 1.987,
          "y_px": 206.667
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-37",
        "text": "\"Just follow ME, just follow ME\"",
        "font": {
          "family": "French Script",
          "size_px": 36
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 3.975,
          "y_px": 222.667
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
